Cargo.lock

# libfuzzer accumulates a per-target corpus under fuzz/corpus/<target>/
# during local runs. CI persists its own corpus via actions/cache, and
# the reusable crate-fuzz workflow re-mines it across runs. We don't
# track the bulk corpus in git (it'd grow unbounded) — only the
# explicit regression seeds checked in via `!` overrides below.
corpus/*
!corpus/panic_free_decode/
corpus/panic_free_decode/*
!corpus/panic_free_decode/golomb-overflow.bin
!corpus/ffmpeg_oracle_decode/
corpus/ffmpeg_oracle_decode/*
!corpus/ffmpeg_oracle_decode/dimension-mismatch-49w.bin
